    "description": "<p>You have achieved the apex in at least some small area of mortal ability. Choose an ability score, combat tradition, or school of magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Ability Score: </strong>When you make an ability check using the chosen ability score and can add your proficiency bonus, you gain an expertise die.</p>\n<p><strong>Combat Tradition: </strong>Attacks you make using combat maneuvers from this tradition gain a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls.</p>\n<p><strong>School of Magic: </strong>When you cast a spell from this school of magic, your spell save DC is treated as 2 higher and you gain a +2 bonus on any spell attack roll it requires.</p>",
